                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 70.9pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);   text-indent: -35.45pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; ">5.2</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; ">We use your data to provide the best possible services to you. This includes:</span></p>

