                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 6pt 0cm 6pt 56.45pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);   text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;  color: rgb(33, 33, 33);">13.2</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box;  color: rgb(33, 33, 33);">the right to complain to a supervisory authority;</span></p>

