                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 6pt 0cm; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);   margin-left: 56px;"> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; ">If you have any questions about Our Site or this Privacy Policy, please contact Us by email at</span><a href="mailto:Fiona@rp-squared.com" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #673ab7; text-decoration-line: none; transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; user-select: auto;"> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; ">Fiona@rp-squared.com</span></a> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; ">, through Our Site&rsquo;s contact form, or by post at</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; ">3905 Two Exchange Square, Suite No 8640, 8 Connaught Place, Central, Hong Kong</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; ">. Please ensure that your query is clear, particularly if it is a request for information about the data We hold about you (as under section 11, above).</span></p>

